import {Box, Typography,Grid,TextField, Paper} from '@mui/material'

export const Details = () => {
  return (
    <Box >
        <Grid container justifyContent={'center'}>

  <Paper
   sx={{padding:'10px',height:'200px'}}
  >
  <Typography >Create Account</Typography>
       
 <Box mt={4}> 
  <Typography  sx={{fontSize:'15px',color:'#E7A452'}}>Account Name</Typography>
  <Box sx={{padding:'5px'}}><input type={'text'} style={{height:'30px',border:'1px solid #cccccc'}} /></Box>
  </Box>
    
  </Paper> 
  </Grid>
</Grid>
        
        </Box>
  )
}
